## Sprint progress
- Sprint 1 (Foundation rebuild): COMPLETE
  - Refactored `src/cli.js` into modules under `src/`.
  - Added dependencies: `cheerio`, `openai`, `@anthropic-ai/sdk`.
  - Added structured proof-point fields and expanded profile preferences.
  - Added REST API scaffold with local CRUD-style routes for core entities.
  - Added local API write protections and sql.js reload-on-request protection.
  - README updated for modular architecture and local-first REST examples.
- Sprint 2 (LLM scoring + tailoring): COMPLETE
  - Implemented provider-backed `src/llm.js.generateJson`.
  - Supported providers/config:
    - `JOBOS_LLM_PROVIDER=openai` via OpenAI-compatible `/chat/completions`.
    - `JOBOS_LLM_PROVIDER=ollama-cloud` via OpenAI-compatible `/chat/completions` defaulting to `https://ollama.com/v1`.
    - `JOBOS_LLM_PROVIDER=anthropic` via `/messages`.
    - `JOBOS_LLM_MODEL`, `JOBOS_LLM_API_KEY`, optional `JOBOS_LLM_BASE_URL`.
  - Replaced scoring with LLM-powered structured JSON output when credentials are configured.
  - Preserved deterministic degraded-mode fallback with explicit `mode: deterministic-degraded` and LLM error capture if provider calls fail.
  - Scoring dimensions now include roleFit, domainFit, seniority, locationWorkModel, compensation, missionInterest, networkAccess, and redFlags with explainable reasoning.
  - Implemented LLM-powered resume/cover-letter tailoring when credentials are configured.
  - Tailoring validates LLM proof mappings against stored proof point IDs and refuses unsupported mappings.
  - Created 5 real-ish eval job fixtures in `tests/eval/jobs/` plus `tests/eval/scoring-cases.json` and `tests/eval/profile-proof-points.md`.
  - Added `tests/sprint2-llm.test.js` covering provider call wiring, authorization header, ≥30 point score differentiation, and proof-grounded tailoring.
  - README updated to document provider-backed LLM scoring/tailoring and degraded-mode fallback.
- Sprint 3 (Research + outreach): NOT STARTED — NEXT
- Sprint 4 (Interview prep + analytics + dashboard): NOT STARTED
- Sprint 5 (Integration + polish + eval): NOT STARTED

